data.description: Take a look at this beautiful gem in the well sought after Meadow Lakes Estates! This beauty has three nice sized bedrooms and two full baths.  This home is modern and well maintained.  It boasts many new updates for your buyers to enjoy.  New  lighting throughout the interior and exterior; new stainless steel appliances; new range hood with an extended back splash; new custom cellular shades; new hot water tank in 2022; new roof and gutters in 2023; freshly painted siding and a new asphalt driveway in 2022 just to name a few of the many updates. This home is truly a diamond. Home shows like a model home. Rare beauty in a great location. Feels like home the moment you walk in.  Make this your new home for the holidays! Agent Owned.
